description:
Is there such a thing as a “true church?” Many churches claim to have the truth, but how can you be sure that they really do? The Bible teaches that there is, in fact, a true church that is solidly grounded on the Word of God.

Join Pastor Ted Wilson as he takes us through the book of Revelation to help us discover God’s truth for today.

Pastor Wilson is sharing Revelation of Hope directly from Indianapolis, IN.
